<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لِذَا اكْتَفَيْتُ أَن أَرَاكِ في الرُّؤَى المُبَشِّرَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>*<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَكَّةُ المُكَرَّمَة * مَدِينَةٌ مُعَظَّمَة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَدْحُهَا يُحِبُّ كُلُّ شَاعِرٍ أَنْ يَنْظِمَه<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قُلُوبُنَا بِحُبِّهَا * مَلِيئَةٌ وَمُفْعَمَة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَحَوْلَ بَيْتِهَا الحَرَامِ رُوحُنَا مُحَوِّمَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{يَاسِرٌ الحَمَدَاني}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَاتِنَةٌ مُهَذَّبَة * مِنْ نَشْوَةٍ مُرَكَّبَة<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَوَسَّدَتْ أَنَامِلِي * وَاسْتَسْلَمَتْ مُلْتَهِبَة<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَعَرْبَدَتْ عَلَى فَمِي * أَنْفَاسُهَا المُضْطَرِبَة<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>تَظَلُّ وَهْيَ في يَدِي * مُبْعَدَةً مُقَرَّبَة<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَكُلَّمَا أَدْنَيْتُهَا * لِلَّحْظَةِ المُسْتَعْذَبَة<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تحْمَرُّ مِن حَيَائِهَا * وَجْنَتُهَا المُخَضَّبَة<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَهَبْتُهَا لِصَاحِبي * فَلَمْ يَرُدَّ لي الهِبَة<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تجِيئُني فِضِّيَّةً * وَتَارَةً مُذَهَّبَة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>كَمْ شُغِلَتْ بِقُبْلَتي * عَنْ رُوحِهَا المُغْتَصَبَة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>